\c 29
\s Rugwaro rwaJeremiya kuvaJudha vakatapwa
\p
\v 1 Zvino awa ndiwo mashoko orugwaro rwakatumwa nomuporofita Jeremiya ari paJerusaremu kuvakuru vakanga vasara kuna vakatapwa, nokuvapristi nokuvaporofita, nokuvanhu vose, vakanga vakatapwa paJerusaremu naNebhukadhinezari, vakaiswa Bhabhironi,
\v 2 Shure kokubva paJerusaremu kwamambo Jekonia, namai vake, navaranda, namachinda aJudha neeJerusaremu, navavezi, navapfuri,
\v 3 noruoko rwaErasa, mwanakomana waShafani, naGemaria, mwanakomana waHirikia, vakanga vatumwa Bhabhironi naZedhekia mambo waJudha kuna Nebhukadhinezari mambo weBhabhironi, achiti,
\p
\v 4 Zvanzi naJehovha wehondo, Mwari waIsiraeri, kuna vose vakatapwa, vandakatapisa Jerusaremu vaiswe Bhabhironi.
\p
\v 5 Zvivakirei dzimba, mugaremo; simai minda, mudye zvibereko zvayo;
\v 6 wanai vakadzi, mubereke vanakomana navanasikana; wanisai vanakomana venyu vakadzi, navanasikana venyu muvaise kuvarume, kuti vabereke vanakomana navanasikana, muwandeko, murege kutapudzwa.
\v 7 Mutsvake rugare rweguta kwandakakutapisai, murinyengeterere kuna Jehovha; nekuti norugare rwaro imwi muchava norugarewo.
\v 8 nekuti zvanzi naJehovha wehondo, Mwari waIsiraeri, Vaporofita venyu, vari pakati penyu, navauki venyu, ngavarege kukunyengerai; regai kuteerera kurota kwenyu kwamunoroteswa.
\p
\v 9 nekuti vanokuporofitirai nhema nezita rangu, ini handina kuvatuma, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\p
\v 10 nekuti zvanzi naJehovha, Kana makore makumi manomwe aperera Bhabhironi, ndichakushanyirai, nokukusimbisirai shoko rangu rakanaka, ndichikudzoserai kunzvimbo ino.
\v 11 nekuti ndinoziva ndangariro dzandinorangarira pamusoro penyu, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha, ndangariro dzorugare, dzisati dziri dzezvakaipa, kuti ndikupei mugumo une tariro.
\v 12 Muchadana kwandiri, muchandonyengetera kwandiri, neni ndichakunzwai.
\v 13 Muchanditsvaka, mukandiwana, kana muchinditsvaka nomoyo wenyu wose.
\v 14 Ndichawanikwa nemi, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha, ndichakudzosai pakutapwa kwenyu, nokukuunganidzai kumarudzi ose, nokunzvimbo dzose kwandakanga ndakudzingirai, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha; ndichakudzoseraizve kunzvimbo kwandakanga ndakutapisai.
\p
\v 15 Zvamakati, Jehovha wakatimutsira vaporofita paBhabhironi;
\v 16 zvanzi naJehovha pamusoro pamambo ugere pachigaro choushe chaDhavhidhi, napamusoro pavanhu vose vagere muguta rino, idzo hama dzenyu dzisina kuenda nemwi pakutapwa kwenyu;
\v 17 zvanzi naJehovha wehondo, Tarirai, ndichatuma pamusoro pavo munondo, nenzara, nehosha yakaipa, ndichavaita samaonde akaipa kwazvo, asingabviri kudyiwa nokuipa kwawo.
\v 18 Ndichateverera nomunondo, nenzara, nehosha yakaipa; ndichavaita chinhu chinotyisa ushe hwose bwenyika, vave chinhu chinotukwa, nechishamiso, nechinoridzirwa muridzo, nechinoshoorwa pakati pamarudzi ose kwandakavadzingira;
\v 19 zvavasina kuteerera mashoko angu, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha, andakatuma kwavari navaranda vangu vaporofita, ndichimuka mangwanani ndichivatuma; asi makaramba kuteerera, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\v 20 Naizvozvo chinzwai shoko raJehovha, imwi mose makatapwa, vandakadzinga paJerusaremu ndikavaisa Bhabhironi.
\p
\v 21 Zvanzi naJehovha wehondo, Mwari waIsiraeri, pamusoro paAhabhi mwanakomana waKoraia, napamusoro paZedhekia mwanakomana waMaaseia, vanokuporofitirai nhema nezita rangu, Tarirai, ndinovaisa muruoko rwaNebhukadhirezari mambo weBhabhironi; iye uchavauraya pamberi penyu;
\v 22 vatapwa vose vaJudha, vari Bhabhironi, vachatora kwavari shoko rokutuka naro, vachiti, Jehovha akuite saZedhekia uye saAhabhi, vakagochwa pamoto namambo weBhabhironi.
\p
\v 23 nekuti vakaita nohupenzi pakati paIsiraeri, vakaita hupombwe navakadzi vovokwavo, vakareva mashoko enhema nezita rangu, andisina kuvaraira; ini ndini ndinoziva, ndini chapupu, ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha.
\p
\v 24 Zvino kuna Shemaia muNeheramite, unofanira kutaura uchiti,
\v 25 Zvanzi naJehovha wehondo, Mwari waIsiraeri, Zvawakatuma magwaro nezita rako kuvanhu vose vari paJerusaremu, nokuna Zefaniya mwanakomana womupristi Maaseia, nokuvapristi vose, uchiti,
\v 26 Jehovha wakakuita mupristi panzvimbo yomupristi Jehoiadha, kuti mumba maJehovha muve navatariri, kuti asunge mumatanda namaketani mumwe nomumwe unopenga, achizviita muporofita.
\p
\v 27 Ko zvino wakaregerei kutuka Jeremiya weAnatoti, unozviita muporofita pamberi penyu,
\v 28 zvaakatuma shoko kwatiri paBhabhironi, achiti, Nguva irefu, vakai dzimba mugaremo; simai minda, mudye zvibereko zvayo?
\p
\v 29 Zvino mupristi Zefaniya akaravira muporofita Jeremiya rugwaro urwu.
\v 30 Ipapo shoko raJehovha rakauya kuna Jeremiya, richiti,
\v 31 Tumira vakatapwa vose shoko rinoti, Zvanzi naJehovha pamusoro paShemaia muNeheramiti, Shemaia zvaakakuporofitirai, ini ndisina kumutuma, akakutendisai nhema,
\v 32 naizvozvo zvanzi naJehovha, Tarirai, ndicharova Shemaia muNeheramiti, navana vake; haangavi nomunhu ungagara pakati pavanhu ava, uye haangaoni zvakanaka zvandichaitira vanhu vangu ndizvo zvinotaura Jehovha nekuti wakataura zvinomukira Jehovha.
